                        "[Turbo Intruder](https://portswigger.net/bappstore/9abaa233088242e8be252cd4ff534988) - High-speed race condition and fuzzing",
                        "[Param Miner](https://portswigger.net/bappstore/17d2949a985c4b7ca092728dba871943) - Discover hidden parameters and cache poisoning",
                        "[HTTP Request Smuggler](https://portswigger.net/bappstore/aaaa60ef945341e8a450217a54a11646) - Automated Request Smuggling tool"
                    ]
                },
